# Day 49 – Personal AI Playbook

## Overview

Today I built **Personal AI Playbook**, an interactive dashboard that helps organize AI workflows, reusable prompt systems, and autonomous prompt loops in one place.

Instead of storing hundreds of individual prompts, the application focuses on creating modular building blocks that can be combined into reusable AI workflows for different tasks.

---

## Features

- Interactive Dashboard
- Personalized Workflow Library
- Prompt Builder with reusable blocks
- Loop Builder for autonomous workflows
- Workflow Categories
- Search & Filter
- Favorite Workflows
- Local Storage Support
- Import & Export Workflow Library (JSON)
- Dark Mode UI
- Responsive Design
- Interactive Help Section

---

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript
- Local Storage API

---

## What I Learned

- Designing reusable AI workflow systems instead of isolated prompts
- Structuring prompts into modular building blocks
- Creating prompt loops for iterative AI tasks
- Organizing workflows with local storage
- Improving dashboard UI/UX for productivity tools

